reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Great size. Nice quality. Multiple ways to mount. Cannot go wrong with this. Metal frame, not plastic.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Poor product and packaing
reviews.reviewText: the frame was completely bent all the way around the mirror. the packing is NOT adequate and clearly does not protect the perimeter of the mirror. I would not purchase this.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 9, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars exactly what I needed
reviews.reviewText: The mirror came packaged well. No scratches and glass in tact. It has a sleek minimalistic look. I’m moving from an apartment into a house and will buy the bigger size of this to go in the new home. You’ll be satisfied with this if you’re looking for something that can go just about anywhere.Note: I didn’t attach it to the wall. I have it leaning. So I can’t say if that portion was difficult or has any issues.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Incorrect measurement and doesn’t have the support “leg” to stand alone
reviews.reviewText: I ordered 64x22, the actual measurement is 61x21 and there were suppose to have two options, mount on wall or stand alone with stand. Only Drew’s for the mounting on wall came with Mirror. I was disappointed in the measurement and the stand miming with the MORROW. I will return today.I gave it two stars because it was well packaged and frame was what I ordered.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Encasing on mirror came damaged.
reviews.reviewText: Arrived Jan 24, 2022. I was very excited to get this mirror. The mirror itself is fine but the reason why I got this was the black iron encasing it looked very elegant. When I got it though, it was crooked and damaged. I tried to see if I can straighten it out myself but unfortunately I can’t. Very disappointed since I paid over $150 for this. Hope the seller contacts me and rectified the situation.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2021
reviews.reviewText: The mirror is not even an option in the site. It has wood around it which is beat up and peeling in spots. There is some red marker on the mirror. Not sure if I’m going to return it or try to fix it up and sell it. Was excited to get this mirror instead received a complete disappointment.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 22, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Manufacturer defect everywhere
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this mirror for my home gym set up and soon as I opened the package, the bevel was in such poor condition as well as the craftsmanship. First thing I noticed was the paint finish coming off in 3 locations(see pics). One corner was already rusting which tells me this company has really poor quality control before sending out to customers. Other immediate observation was the paint finish itself. I bought the wrought black iron finish. This is not wrought but just plain poor craftsmanship. Pictures speak for itself and you can immediately see that this is not worth the money spent, not even at half price would I be happy about this mirror. I called Amazon immediately to get a refund for this poor quality product. Be warned.
